data.title: Adelais "Adelaide de Poitiers" de Poitou reine des Francs (± 952
data.meta_description: Adelais de Poitou was born about 950 TO ABT 952 in Ducjy de Aquitaine (now Aquitaine, France), daughter of Guillaume 'Tête d'étoupe' d'Aquitaine and Geirlaug Adèle Hrólfsdóttir de Normandie. She was married about 968 to Hugues 'Capet' roi des Francs roi des Francs, they had 3 children. She died about 1004 TO ABT 1006 in Paris, Orleannais, West Francia (now Ile-de-France, France). This information is part of Family tree Homs by George Homs on Genealogy Online.
